description: Certain subgraphs of a directed graph.
references: N. J. A. Sloane and Simon Plouffe, The Encyclopedia of Integer Sequences, Academic Press, 1995 (includes this sequence).
links: E. Andresen, K. Kjeldsen, On certain subgraphs of a complete transitively directed graph, Discrete Math. 14 (1976), no. 2, 103-119.
formula: G.f.: Sum(x^n*Product((2^i-1)/(1+(2^i-2)*x),i = 1 .. n),n = 0 .. infinity). - _Vladeta Jovovic_, Mar 10 2008
author: _N. J. A. Sloane_
